      <title>罗斯·格伯称 Netflix 的盈利是“双赢”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-21/netflix-earnings-are-a-double-win-ross-gerber-says-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Gerber Kawasaki Wealth and Investment Management 联合创始人兼首席执行官 Ross Gerber 在“Bloomberg The Close”节目中对 Netflix 的季度收益和用户增长做出了反应。Netflix 在 2024 年收盘时创下了历史上最大的季度用户增长，这得益于其首次直播大型体育赛事和“鱿鱼游戏”的回归。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-21/netflix-earnings-are-a-double-win-ross-gerber-says-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 22:17:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
